            "descriptionRaw": "Performing the secret hand seals, Chongyun summons 3 giant spirit blades in mid-air that fall to the earth one by one after a short delay, exploding as they hit the ground.\nWhen the spirit blades explode, they will deal <color=#99FFFFFF>AoE Cryo DMG</color> and launch opponents.\n\n<i>\"As ice doth give the biting frost birth, My transcendent blade shakes heaven and earth. Heed my summons and come hence!\"</i>",
            "name": "Spirit Blade: Cloud-Parting Star"
        },
